Activate this card by declaring an Attribute; equip only to a "Shaddoll" monster. The Attribute of the equipped monster becomes the declared Attribute. If you control the equipped monster and this card: You can Fusion Summon 1 "Shaddoll" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, using monsters from your hand or your side of the field as Fusion Materials, including the equipped monster you control. You can only use this effect of "Nepheshaddoll Fusion" once per turn.
